! STEOM-CCSD cc-pVDZ TightSCF
# Realistic reference: formaldehyde n->pi* should be ~3.9-4.0 eV (canonical STEOM,
# close to EOM-CCSD/experiment ~3.94 eV). Default automatic active space.
# This is the production-setting number to compare GANSU STEOM against
# (GANSU reportedly gives ~1.48 eV here = the real bug).
%mdci
  nroots 6
  DoSTEOM true
end
